{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01JLf1n1tmLRcVV8EQ8TGxTG","type":"tool_result","content":"variable\tvalue\tdefault_value\tdescription\nsql.defaults.cost_scans_with_default_col_size.enabled\tfalse\tfalse\tsetting to true uses the same size for all columns to compute scan cost\nsql.defaults.datestyle\tiso, mdy\tiso, mdy\tdefault value for DateStyle session setting [iso, mdy = 0, iso, dmy = 1, iso, ymd = 2]\nsql.defaults.default_hash_sharded_index_bucket_count\t16\t16\tused as bucket count if bucket count is not specified in hash sharded index definition\nsql.defaults.default_int_size\t8\t8\tthe size, in bytes, of an INT type\nsql.defaults.disallow_full_table_scans.enabled\tfalse\tfalse\tsetting to true rejects queries that have planned a full table scan\nsql.defaults.distsql\tauto\tauto\tdefault distributed SQL execution mode [off = 0, auto = 1, on = 2, always = 3]\nsql.defaults.experimental_alter_column_type.enabled\tfalse\tfalse\tdefault value for experimental_alter_column_type session setting; enables the use of ALTER COLUMN TYPE for general conversions\nsql.defaults.experimental_auto_rehoming.enabled\tfalse\tfalse\tdefault value for experimental_enable_auto_rehoming; allows for rows in REGIONAL BY ROW tables to be auto-rehomed on UPDATE\nsql.defaults.experimental_computed_column_rewrites\t\t\tallows rewriting computed column expressions in CREATE TABLE and ALTER TABLE statements; the format is: '(before expression) -> (after expression) [, (before expression) -> (after expression) ...]'\nsql.defaults.experimental_distsql_planning\toff\toff\tdefault experimental_distsql_planning mode; enables experimental opt-driven DistSQL planning [off = 0, on = 1]\nsql.defaults.experimental_enable_unique_without_index_constraints.enabled\tfalse\tfalse\tdefault value for experimental_enable_unique_without_index_constraints session setting;disables unique without index constraints by default\nsql.defaults.experimental_implicit_column_partitioning.enabled\tfalse\tfalse\tdefault value for experimental_enable_temp_tables; allows for the use of implicit column partitioning\nsql.defaults.experimental_temporary_tables.enabled\tfalse\tfalse\tdefault value for experimental_enable_temp_tables; allows for use of temporary tables by default\nsql.defaults.foreign_key_cascades_limit\t10000\t10000\tdefault value for foreign_key_cascades_limit session setting; limits the number of cascading operations that run as part of a single query\nsql.defaults.idle_in_session_timeout\t0s\t0s\tdefault value for the idle_in_session_timeout; default value for the idle_in_session_timeout session setting; controls the duration a session is permitted to idle before the session is terminated; if set to 0, there is no timeout\nsql.defaults.idle_in_transaction_session_timeout\t0s\t0s\tdefault value for the idle_in_transaction_session_timeout; controls the duration a session is permitted to idle in a transaction before the session is terminated; if set to 0, there is no timeout\nsql.defaults.implicit_select_for_update.enabled\ttrue\ttrue\tdefault value for enable_implicit_select_for_update session setting; enables FOR UPDATE locking during the row-fetch phase of mutation statements\nsql.defaults.insert_fast_path.enabled\ttrue\ttrue\tdefault value for enable_insert_fast_path session setting; enables a specialized insert path\nsql.defaults.intervalstyle\tpostgres\tpostgres\tdefault value for IntervalStyle session setting [postgres = 0, iso_8601 = 1, sql_standard = 2]\nsql.defaults.large_full_scan_rows\t1000\t1000\tdefault value for large_full_scan_rows session setting which determines the maximum table size allowed for a full scan when disallow_full_table_scans is set to true\nsql.defaults.locality_optimized_partitioned_index_scan.enabled\ttrue\ttrue\tdefault value for locality_optimized_partitioned_index_scan session setting; enables searching for rows in the current region before searching remote regions\nsql.defaults.lock_timeout\t0s\t0s\tdefault value for the lock_timeout; default value for the lock_timeout session setting; controls the duration a query is permitted to wait while attempting to acquire a lock on a key or while blocking on an existing lock in order to perform a non-locking read on a key; if set to 0, there is no timeout\nsql.defaults.multiregion_placement_policy.enabled\tfalse\tfalse\tdefault value for enable_multiregion_placement_policy; allows for use of PLACEMENT RESTRICTED\nsql.defaults.on_update_rehome_row.enabled\ttrue\ttrue\tdefault value for on_update_rehome_row; enables ON UPDATE rehome_row() expressions to trigger on updates\nsql.defaults.optimizer_use_histograms.enabled\ttrue\ttrue\tdefault value for optimizer_use_histograms session setting; enables usage of histograms in the optimizer by default\nsql.defaults.optimizer_use_multicol_stats.enabled\ttrue\ttrue\tdefault value for optimizer_use_multicol_stats session setting; enables usage of multi-column stats in the optimizer by default\nsql.defaults.override_alter_primary_region_in_super_region.enabled\tfalse\tfalse\tdefault value for override_alter_primary_region_in_super_region; allows for altering the primary region even if the primary region is a member of a super region\nsql.defaults.override_multi_region_zone_config.enabled\tfalse\tfalse\tdefault value for override_multi_region_zone_config; allows for overriding the zone configs of a multi-region table or database\nsql.defaults.prefer_lookup_joins_for_fks.enabled\tfalse\tfalse\tdefault value for prefer_lookup_joins_for_fks session setting; causes foreign key operations to use lookup joins when possible\nsql.defaults.primary_region\t\t\tif not empty, all databases created without a PRIMARY REGION will implicitly have the given PRIMARY REGION\nsql.defaults.propagate_input_ordering.enabled\tfalse\tfalse\tdefault value for the experimental propagate_input_ordering session variable\nsql.defaults.reorder_joins_limit\t8\t8\tdefault number of joins to reorder\nsql.defaults