{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_012gBjMEktvRyB27HBgGnf1a","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01WZRsqzDtJ32L5BGyJACSBq","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"cat > /tmp/findings.txt << 'FINDINGS_EOF'\nCockroachDB Compliance Audit Report\nAudit Date: 2026-06-23\nCluster Version: v24.1.0 (CockroachDB CCL, built 2024/05/15)\nClusterID: 90e1175c-3ef3-4b10-a3e4-c23d7c62a860\nNamespace: cockroachdb\nAudited By: KARMA automated audit (read-only)\n\n==============================================================================\n1. NODE COUNT AND CLUSTER HEALTH\n==============================================================================\n\nStatefulSet: crdb-cluster — Replicas: 3/3 READY\nImage: cockroachdb/cockroach:v24.1.0\n\nNode Status (all nodes available and live):\n  Node 1: crdb-cluster-0.crdb-cluster.cockroachdb.svc.cluster.local:26257\n    Started: 2026-06-23 17:36:52 UTC | Last Updated: 2026-06-23 17:37:43 UTC\n    is_available=true, is_live=true\n  Node 2: crdb-cluster-1.crdb-cluster.cockroachdb.svc.cluster.local:26257\n    Started: 2026-06-23 17:22:46 UTC | Last Updated: 2026-06-23 17:37:43 UTC\n    is_available=true, is_live=true\n  Node 3: crdb-cluster-2.crdb-cluster.cockroachdb.svc.cluster.local:26257\n    Started: 2026-06-23 17:21:47 UTC | Last Updated: 2026-06-23 17:37:45 UTC\n    is_available=true, is_live=true\n\nOverall Health: HEALTHY — all 3 nodes live and available.\n\n==============================================================================\n2. NON-DEFAULT CLUSTER SETTINGS\n==============================================================================\n\nThe following settings differ from their factory defaults:\n\n  kv.snapshot_rebalance.max_rate\n    Current:  208 MiB\n    Default:  32 MiB\n    Impact:   Rebalance snapshot bandwidth increased ~6.5x. Speeds up\n              rebalancing but increases network load during rebalance events.\n\n  kv.range_merge.queue.enabled\n    Current:  false\n    Default:  true\n    Impact:   Range merge queue is disabled. Ranges will not be automatically\n              merged when they fall below the minimum size threshold.\n\n  diagnostics.reporting.enabled\n    Current:  true\n    Default:  false\n    Impact:   Cluster sends diagnostic/telemetry data to Cockroach Labs.\n\n  version (internal)\n    Current:  24.1 (cluster finalized version)\n\n  cluster.secret (internal UUID, not a tunable)\n\nAll sql.defaults.* settings are at their factory defaults (no custom SQL\nsession defaults have been applied at the cluster level).\n\n==============================================================================\n3. ZONE CONFIGURATIONS\n==============================================================================\n\n3a. Built-in System Ranges\n--------------------------\n\nRANGE default\n  range_min_bytes = 134217728 (128 MiB)\n  range_max_bytes = 536870912 (512 MiB)\n  gc.ttlseconds   = 14400  (4 hours)\n  num_replicas    = 3\n  constraints     = []\n  lease_preferences = []\n\nRANGE meta\n  range_min_bytes = 134217728 (128 MiB)\n  range_max_bytes = 536870912 (512 MiB)\n  gc.ttlseconds   = 3600  (1 hour)\n  num_replicas    = 5\n  constraints     = []\n  lease_preferences = []\n\nRANGE system\n  range_min_bytes = 134217728 (128 MiB)\n  range_max_bytes = 536870912 (512 MiB)\n  gc.ttlseconds   = 14400  (4 hours)\n  num_replicas    = 5\n  constraints     = []\n  lease_preferences = []\n\nRANGE liveness\n  range_min_bytes = 134217728 (128 MiB)\n  range_max_bytes = 536870912 (512 MiB)\n  gc.ttlseconds   = 600  (10 minutes)\n  num_replicas    = 5\n  constraints     = []\n  lease_preferences = []\n\n3b. System Database Zone\n------------------------\n\nDATABASE system\n  range_min_bytes = 134217728 (128 MiB)\n  range_max_bytes = 536870912 (512 MiB)\n  gc.ttlseconds   = 14400  (4 hours)\n  num_replicas    = 5\n  constraints     = []\n  lease_preferences = []\n\n3c. System Table Overrides (GC TTL only)\n-----------------------------------------\n\nTABLE system.public.lease\n  gc.ttlseconds = 600  (10 minutes)\n\nTABLE system.public.replication_constraint_stats\n  gc.ttlseconds = 600  (10 minutes)\n\nTABLE system.public.replication_stats\n  gc.ttlseconds = 600  (10 minutes)\n\nTABLE system.public.statement_statistics\n  gc.ttlseconds = 3600  (1 hour)\n\nTABLE system.public.transaction_statistics\n  gc.ttlseconds = 3600  (1 hour)\n\nTABLE system.public.statement_activity\n  gc.ttlseconds = 3600  (1 hour)\n\nTABLE system.public.transaction_activity\n  gc.ttlseconds = 3600  (1 hour)\n\nTABLE system.public.tenant_usage\n  gc.ttlseconds = 7200  (2 hours)\n\nTABLE system.public.span_stats_tenant_boundaries\n  gc.ttlseconds = 3600  (1 hour)\n\n3d. User Table Zone Configurations (NON-DEFAULT — key finding)\n--------------------------------------------------------------\n\nTABLE defaultdb.tenant_b.table_c\n  range_min_bytes = 134217728 (128 MiB)\n  range_max_bytes = 536870912 (512 MiB)\n  gc.ttlseconds   = 14400  (4 hours)\n  num_replicas    = 3\n\nTABLE defaultdb.tenant_b.table_d\n  range_min_bytes = 134217728 (128 MiB)\n  range_max_bytes = 536870912 (512 MiB)\n  gc.ttlseconds   = 14400  (4 hours)\n  num_replicas    = 3\n\nNote: Tables defaultdb.tenant_a.table_a and defaultdb.tenant_a.table_b have NO\nexplicit zone config and inherit from RANGE default (num_replicas=3,\ngc.ttlseconds=14400).\n\n==============================================================================\n4. REPLICATION FACTOR SUMMARY\n==============================================================================\n\n  RANGE default (user data baseline):  num_replicas = 3\n  RANGE meta:                           num_replicas = 5\n  RANGE system:                         num_replicas = 5\n  RANGE liveness:                       num_replicas = 5\n  DATABASE system:                      num_replicas = 5\n  defaultdb.tenant_b.table_c:          num_replicas = 3 (explicit, matches default)\n  defaultdb.tenant_b.table_d: 